cf9a8461\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190811/s00001/1565495373929/【逃犯條例】新加坡高官-意識形態固然重要-但必須符合現實</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">世上是否有另一個政治制度，能夠比現有的制度更好地造福中國人民？有哪一個制度能夠做到？你能舉出一個例子嗎？那麼，誰的制度比較好呢？由此可見，意識形態固然重要，卻必須符合現實</span><br />\n<br />\n同支那人D論調一樣<br />\n冇民主冇自由<br />\n然後話民主自由唔好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4fbab9e6b4720c27b5e156a4622d20ca2b3da9","tid":1442800,"uid":61111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"新加坡只係一個大型監獄 響果度做過一段時間野 PR都唔撚想要 辭職走人 狗也不屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8122b5a1b76621b23454af4152ea24dd69b618","tid":1442800,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"新加坡幾時回歸祖國既懷抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bae1b746e5b6a527ca3b4809951a3f42e2b5cb2","tid":1442800,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cd8065779196cf2ccd76e365412f7db88814d7","tid":1442800,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"中屬新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/choa-chu-kang-town-council-lodges-police-report-after-chinas-flag-displayed-at-hdb-block?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=STFB&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR2CHzF1GP4kVnPkkouhJt7wLYLIWT-6bZ1o5DDUjE93AdGHIV7mNKvfxuo#Echobox=1565191193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fsingapore%2Fchoa-chu-kang-town-council-lodges-police-report-after-chinas-flag-displayed-at-hdb-block%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_campaign%3DSTFB%26utm_source%3DFacebook%26fbclid%3